metadata.name: ://MANY-FOLD
metadata.description:
iAM hoidok619 and I am a web3 digital artist that loves pepe, memes, pets and using art to connect with people globally. 

After an AMA with Apelist, Pukecast & Rug Radio (check twitter) I have explained my plans with MAP and how I want to bring art and value to holders starting with “://THE CREATION OF GM3.0”. 

But before that, I present to you an OE titled “://MANY-FOLD” 

This OE will be the First edition of my MAP series and a snapshot will be taken to give 3 AL spots for “://THE CREATION OF GM3.0”. Also, for those who have “MANYFOLDS”, I will explore the burning mechanism soon for various editions or perks within the grand ecosystem. 

”://MANY-FOLD” is my collage attempt of manifold.xyz , memefi’ing them along with MANY-FOLDING a number of respectable communities I love. 

This is truly life changing for me as it is a new approach in how I express myself and artwork within the web3 space. I definitely have plans to provide more value to those within the MAP ecosystem and branching out into more things moving forward. 

Much love and thank you everyone for your love and support. Kindly share your minted OE of “://MANY-FOLD” and tag me on twitter and let’s get the MAP community together, strong. booyah !! 

Y’all are amazing. Thank you.
